      <title>Handbook for Culturally Competent Care</title>
      <para>Editors</para>
      <para>Eric A. Fenkl</para>
      <para>and</para>
      <para>Larry D. Purnell</para>
      <para>Second Edition 2024</para>
      <figure float="0" id="pr0002s0001fg01" role="Figure">
         <title/>
         <mediaobject>
            <imageobject>
               <imagedata fileref="Prefacef01.jpg" scalefit="1" width="100%"/>
            </imageobject>
         </mediaobject>
      </figure>
      <para>Editors</para>
      <para>Eric A. Fenkl</para>
      <para role="AffiliationText">Nicole Wertheim College of Nursing and Health Sciences, Florida International University, Miami, FL, USA</para>
      <para>Larry D. Purnell</para>
      <para role="AffiliationText">College of Health and Nursing Sciences, Excelsior University, Albany, NY, USA</para>
      <para role="CopyrightPageISBNs">ISBN 978-3-031-70491-8<?lb?>e-ISBN 978-3-031-70492-5</para>
      <para>
         <ulink url="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-031-70492-5">https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-031-70492-5</ulink>
      </para>
      <para>© The Editor(s) (if applicable) and The Author(s), under exclusive license to Springer Nature Switzerland AG 2019, 2024</para>
      <para>corrected publication</para>
      <para>2024</para>
