         <title>
            <emphasis role="HeadingNumber">13.2 </emphasis> Reflective Exercises</title>
         <orderedlist continuation="restarts" inheritnum="ignore">
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What is the most common languages spoken by Filipinos? What is <emphasis>Taglish</emphasis>?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What is meant by “Filipino time?”</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Describe the name format for Filipinos.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Describe Filipino communication practices.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are the most common health conditions of Filipinos?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are acceptable birth control practices for <emphasis>traditional</emphasis> Filipinos?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Describe at least three prenatal beliefs about pregnancy.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What is a <emphasis>hilot</emphasis>?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What healing rituals are used for a child with the “evil eye”?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>To what might Filipinos attribute mental illness?</para>
            </listitem>
         </orderedlist>
      </sect1>
