                  <surname>Fenkl</surname>
               </personname>
            </primaryauthor>
         </sect1info>
         <title>
            <emphasis role="HeadingNumber">16.2 </emphasis> Reflective Exercises</title>
         <orderedlist continuation="restarts" inheritnum="ignore">
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Explain the name format for Guatemalans at birth and at matrimony.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What languages besides Spanish are spoken by Guatemalans and Mayans?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Explain the concept of “evil eye”. What could one do to break a spell of the “evil eye”?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Explain common infectious diseases among Guatemalan natives? What resources could be suggested to increase disease prevention?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are common eye problems among Guatemalans? What are some reasons for these eye problems?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Identify common birthing practices that are used by women of Guatemalan heritage?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What folk illnesses are common among Guatemalans and Mayans?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What routes do Guatemalans prefer for medication administration?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>If a Guatemalan dies in the United States (and probably elsewhere) and the family wants to have the body returned to Guatemala, what resources are available to assist the family?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>How is <emphasis>fatalism</emphasis> displayed among Guatemalans?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>How would you assess jaundice, cyanosis, and petechiae in dark-skinned Guatemalans?</para>
            </listitem>
         </orderedlist>
      </sect1>
      <sect1 id="ch0016s0003" role="bibliography">
         <sect1info>
