         <title>
            <emphasis role="HeadingNumber">19.2 </emphasis> Reflective Exercises</title>
         <orderedlist continuation="restarts" inheritnum="ignore">
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>When and under what conditions did the Hmong people begin immigrating to the US?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What languages do the Hmong speak? How can you obtain an interpreter for a Hmong individual who does not speak English?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Who makes healthcare decisions in Hmong society?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are at least five diseases and health conditions that are common among the Hmong community?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What concerns might you have for a Hmong patient who practices animism?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What conditions do Hmong traditional healthcare providers treat?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Identify postpartum dietary practices among Hmong women.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What symptoms would you observe in a patient who practices “cupping” and “coining”?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are some stressors that contribute to mental health conditions among the Hmong community?</para>
            </listitem>
         </orderedlist>
      </sect1>
