            <bibliomixed id="ch0023s0003bib06">Campbell A (2018) The Jamaican public healthcare system from the 17th-21st centuries: a policy and structural perspective. University of Technology, Jamaica Press</bibliomixed>
            <bibliomixed id="ch0023s0003bib07">Cassells ED, de Carvalho G, Frisina Doetter L (2022) The colonial legacy and the Jamaican healthcare system. In: International impacts on social policy: short histories in global perspective. Springer, Cham, pp 89–103<bibliomisc>
