         </sect1info>
         <title>
            <emphasis role="HeadingNumber">28.2 </emphasis> Reflective Exercises</title>
         <orderedlist continuation="restarts" inheritnum="ignore">
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Describe Polish communication practices as they relate to the practice of using the third person.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What do Poles expect in terms of timeliness?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Describe taboo behaviors for Polish children.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Name and describe at least three diseases common among Poles.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are some of the foods a Pole might eat?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Describe some prescriptive and restrictive Polish prenatal/postpartum practices.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What might you do to encourage a stoic Pole to accept pain medication?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>How is mental illness perceived by Poles?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Identify at least three common folk remedies commonly used by Polish people.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Describe a traditional Polish funeral.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Post-COVID, how have health, social, and economic services changed in Poland?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What measures will the Ministry of Health implement to improve COVID vaccination rates in Poland with Poles and Ukrainians?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Why is Ukraine important to Poland?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What is the current impact on Poland because of the Russian-Ukrainian war?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What will the Ministry of Health leadership and government officials implement to improve culturally competent care in Poland?</para>
            </listitem>
         </orderedlist>
      </sect1>
