                  <surname>Fenkl</surname>
               </personname>
            </primaryauthor>
         </sect1info>
         <title>
            <emphasis role="HeadingNumber">31.2 </emphasis> Reflective Exercises</title>
         <orderedlist continuation="restarts" inheritnum="ignore">
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What do Somali people speak as their primary language? Where might you find an interpreter for this group?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>How would you greet a Somali male patient? A Somali female patient?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Explain decision-making practices among the Somali people. What implications does this have for your nursing care?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are the primary non-communicable health conditions among Somalis? What might you do to help decrease some of them?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Name at least three infectious conditions common among Somali immigrants. What are the implications for your initial assessment and follow-up care?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Explain the name format for Somali men. For Somali Women.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Identify infant feeding beliefs among Somali families. What educational advice would you offer?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What is the dominant religious practice among Somalis? How does this affect your care?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>How is depression seen among Somalis? What is your approach to addressing depression?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Identify several traditional healthcare practices. How might you incorporate traditional healers with allopathic treatments?</para>
            </listitem>
         </orderedlist>
      </sect1>
      <sect1 id="ch0031s0003" role="bibliography">
         <sect1info>
