               <personname>
                  <firstname>Eric A.</firstname>
                  <surname>Fenkl</surname>
               </personname>
            </primaryauthor>
         </sect1info>
         <title>
            <emphasis role="HeadingNumber">32.2 </emphasis> Reflective Exercises</title>
         <orderedlist continuation="restarts" inheritnum="ignore">
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are the three main dialects spoken in Thailand? How might you get an interpreter for each dialect?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are nonverbal practices used by Thais?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Identify at least two genetic conditions common among Thais. What implications do they have for health and health teaching?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Identify common health conditions among Thais.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What is <emphasis>Tom-Yum</emphasis>? What are the ingredients and what are its health properties? For what conditions is it advantageous?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>6. <emphasis>Som-tum</emphasis>? What are the ingredients and what are its health properties? For what conditions is it advantageous?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What foods might be avoided among some Thai postpartum women? Why are these foods avoided?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What is the dominant religion of Thais? What are its principles?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Identify several Thai folk practices. For what conditions are they used?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are the roles of men and women in traditional Thai culture?</para>
            </listitem>
         </orderedlist>
      </sect1>
