               <personname>
                  <firstname>Eric A.</firstname>
                  <surname>Fenkl</surname>
               </personname>
            </primaryauthor>
         </sect1info>
         <title>
            <emphasis role="HeadingNumber">34.2 </emphasis> Reflective Exercises</title>
         <orderedlist continuation="restarts" inheritnum="ignore">
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are traditional verbal and nonverbal communications practices in Ukrainian culture?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>How do Ukrainians value their time and punctuality?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are the decision-making practices in current Ukrainian immigrants?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>List one healthcare condition in Ukrainians in each of the three categories: environment, lifestyle, and genetics. What can you do to decrease the incidence and prevalence of these diseases?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are common high-risk health behaviors in Ukrainian immigrants? Include some strategies for reducing them.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are fertility control practices in Ukrainians? What education would you provide to the family about childbirth and contraception practices?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Many Ukrainians are not seeking psychiatric care. What is a reason for this? What can you do to decrease their fear?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Identify traditional folk treatments. How would you know that this treatment is being used?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Identify some practices women use during pregnancy.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Identify some cultural traditional Ukrainian practices. Which of them might have harmful effects?</para>
            </listitem>
         </orderedlist>
      </sect1>
