                  <surname>Fenkl</surname>
               </personname>
            </primaryauthor>
         </sect1info>
         <title>
            <emphasis role="HeadingNumber">35.2 </emphasis> Reflective Exercises</title>
         <orderedlist continuation="restarts" inheritnum="ignore">
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Explain the naming format for Vietnamese men and women.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>When does a traditional Vietnamese have a birthday? What might this mean for child development in accordance with the US standards and expectations?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>What are traditional Vietnamese family roles and decision-making?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Describe two high-risk health behaviors that may require additional screening during a health care intervention.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>List five ideologies or ideals that Vietnamese people value as part of the culture.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Explain the <emphasis>am</emphasis> and <emphasis>duong</emphasis> concepts of nutrition.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>How do <emphasis>am</emphasis> and <emphasis>duong</emphasis> practices vary with pregnancy and postpartum practices?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>How are the principles of <emphasis>am</emphasis> and <emphasis>duong</emphasis> displayed in illnesses?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>How are mental illnesses seen among the Vietnamese? As a health-care provider, what can you do to improve Vietnamese’s’ access to mental health professionals?</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem role="ListItem">
               <para>Explain the five different traditional Vietnamese medical practices.</para>
            </listitem>
         </orderedlist>
      </sect1>
